name: Mobilization Points
Lore: 'The imperial noose relies on swift troop dispatch from docking bays.',
Text: 'Deploy on table. Your Force generation is +1 at each docking bay you occupy (or +2 if you control). Once per game, you may take one Carida, Wakeelmui, Gall, Kuat or Rendili system or Executor into hand from Reserve Deck; reshuffle. (Immune to Alter.)',
